sequenceDiagram
  actor C as Candidate
  participant SPA as SPA
  participant API as CandidateJobs API
  participant DB as DB
  C->>SPA: Apply to published job
  SPA->>API: POST application
  API->>DB: Enforce ownership + duplicate check
  alt duplicate
    API-->>SPA: 409 Conflict
  else ok
    API->>DB: Insert Application + history + notification
    API-->>SPA: 201 Created
  end
